上下文: '[记忆片段 #1]\n4:33 pm on 12 July, 2023\nMelanie: Wow, Caroline! Books have such an awesome power! Which one has been your favorite guide?\n\n[记忆片段 #2]\n8:18 pm on 6 July, 2023\nCaroline: Wow, that\'s great! It sure shows how important friendship and compassion are. It\'s made me appreciate how lucky I am to have my friends and family helping with my transition. They make all the difference. We even had a picnic last week!\n\n[记忆片段 #3]\n4:33 pm on 12 July, 2023\nCaroline: I loved "Becoming Nicole" by Amy Ellis Nutt. It\'s a real inspiring true story about a trans girl and her family. It made me feel connected and gave me a lot of hope for my own path. Highly recommend it for sure!\n\n[记忆片段 #4]\n1:51 pm on 15 July, 2023\nCaroline: No worries, Mel! Your friendship means so much to me. Enjoy your day!\n\n[记忆片段 #5]\n8:18 pm on 6 July, 2023\nMelanie: I loved reading "Charlotte\'s Web" as a kid. It was so cool seeing how friendship and compassion can make a difference.\n\n[记忆片段 #6]\n1:51 pm on 15 July, 2023\nMelanie: Thanks, Caroline! Appreciate your friendship. It\'s great to have a supporter!\n\n[记忆片段 #7]\n1:50 pm on 17 August, 2023\nMelanie: I appreciate our friendship too, Caroline. You\'ve always been there for me.'
