上下文: "[记忆片段 #1]\n10:37 am on 27 June, 2023\nCaroline: Hey Melanie! Long time no talk! A lot's been going on in my life! Take a look at this.\n\n[记忆片段 #2]\n2:31 pm on 17 July, 2023\nMelanie: Caroline, awesome news that you two are getting along! What was it like for you both? Care to fill me in?\n\n[记忆片段 #3]\n8:18 pm on 6 July, 2023\nCaroline: Wow, that's great! It sure shows how important friendship and compassion are. It's made me appreciate how lucky I am to have my friends and family helping with my transition. They make all the difference. We even had a picnic last week!\n\n[记忆片段 #4]\n1:50 pm on 17 August, 2023\nMelanie: Yeah, Caroline! I'll start thinking about what we can do.\n\n[记忆片段 #5]\n1:50 pm on 17 August, 2023\nMelanie: I appreciate our friendship too, Caroline. You've always been there for me.\n\n[记忆片段 #6]\n3:19 pm on 28 August, 2023\nCaroline: Cool! Got any fav tunes?\n\n[记忆片段 #7]\n8:18 pm on 6 July, 2023\nMelanie: Glad you have support, Caroline! Unconditional love is so important. Here's a pic of my family camping at the beach. We love it, it brings us closer!"
