上下文: "[记忆片段 #1]\n8:17 pm on 21 September, 2023\nJohn: Yeah, something cool happened! I attended a local restaurant with some new teammates last week. It was great getting to know them better.\n\n[记忆片段 #2]\n7:54 pm on 17 August, 2023\nJohn: Hey Tim! We had a wild few days since we talked. I met back up with my teammates on the 15th after my trip and it was amazing! Everyone missed me. The atmosphere was electric and I felt so welcome being back with them. I'm so lucky to be a part of this team!\n\n[记忆片段 #3]\n6:59 pm on 26 August, 2023\nJohn: We were teammates for four years in high school, so we've played together for quite some time. Have you ever been part of a sports team?\n\n[记忆片段 #4]\n4:21 pm on 16 July, 2023\nJohn: Definitely! Being surrounded by teammates who are equally passionate creates a strong bond. We push each other to be our best and the love for the game is infectious. It's like having a second family.\n\n[记忆片段 #5]\n7:54 pm on 17 August, 2023\nJohn: You're a real bookworm! It would be awesome to go to a book conference with you. Check out this photo of what my teammates gave me when we met. It's a sign of our friendship and all the love we have for each other.\n\n[记忆片段 #6]\n3:37 pm on 16 December, 2023\nJohn: Yeah, I injured myself not too long ago. It sucked because I had to miss some games and couldn't help my team.\n\n[记忆片段 #7]\n5:51 pm on 21 October, 2023\nJohn: Yeah, definitely! That's my fam hanging out. Being with them brings me so much happiness and helps me remember what's important. My team is like my second family too."
